WEBVTT

00:00:00.253 --> 00:00:03.018
"Fruit"

00:00:03.018 --> 00:00:04.495
(Notice of Adjunct Teacher Appointment Termination)

00:00:04.495 --> 00:00:07.013
(Episode 8: Suppression)

00:00:09.937 --> 00:00:11.860
(Dear Miss Zhang Ronghua,)

00:00:11.860 --> 00:00:14.557
(following a resolution by the school committee...)

00:00:14.557 --> 00:00:16.684
(your contract will not be renewed upon expiration.)

00:00:41.733 --> 00:00:43.200
Here...

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:44.833
her presence lingers.

00:00:46.870 --> 00:00:48.900
The air she breathed is still here.

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:24.600
Miss,

00:01:25.505 --> 00:01:27.100
how should I draw this part?

00:01:27.966 --> 00:01:30.100
Only when I'm about to leave

00:01:31.466 --> 00:01:32.766
do I realize

00:01:33.466 --> 00:01:35.800
she has already taken over my world.

00:01:35.800 --> 00:01:37.260
You're peeking at me drawing again.

00:01:39.566 --> 00:01:41.233
I wasn't peeking.

00:01:41.966 --> 00:01:45.400
I just wanted to know... what you were doing.

00:01:49.100 --> 00:01:50.200
Miss,

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:51.800
you walk so silently!

00:01:51.800 --> 00:01:53.433
It's not that I walk silently.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:01:59.266
I just didn't want to startle you.

00:02:08.700 --> 00:02:11.833
Miss, you look really tired today.

00:02:12.641 --> 00:02:13.933
It's not that I'm tired,

00:02:17.117 --> 00:02:18.433
it's feeling drained

00:02:20.533 --> 00:02:22.600
at the thought of leaving you.

00:02:23.566 --> 00:02:25.333
Miss,

00:02:25.333 --> 00:02:27.444
you need to take care of yourself.

00:02:28.166 --> 00:02:29.366
Miss,

00:02:30.300 --> 00:02:32.066
are you okay?

00:02:48.100 --> 00:02:49.707
Can I just...

00:02:52.133 --> 00:02:55.033
stop holding on all by myself?

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:16.100
Miss.

00:03:46.066 --> 00:03:48.033
I know full well it's forbidden.

00:03:48.900 --> 00:03:50.866
But when it comes to feelings,

00:03:51.566 --> 00:03:54.200
why do they never ask if the timing is right?

00:04:25.733 --> 00:04:28.300
Stopping here... is for the best.